 |title        = Eadgifu [Eddeua] the Fair [the Rich] (fl. 1066), magnate
 |year         = 2004
 |url          = http://www.oxforddnb.com/view/article/52349/?back=,12360
 |accessdate   = 19 March 2014
 |doi          = 10.1093/ref:odnb/52349
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924160038/http://www.oxforddnb.com/view/article/52349/?back=,12360
 |archive-date = 2015-09-24
 |dead-url     = yes
}} {{ODNBsub}}</ref>。她常被后人称作“'''天鹅颈伊迪丝'''”（Edith Swanneck/Swan-Neck，{{lang|ang|Ealdgȳð Swann hnecca}}），但这个称呼是后世的讹传<ref>{{cite book
